<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2026 13:01:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>空射无人机是防止新型陆军侦察机受到伤害的关键</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/air-launched-drones-key-to-keeping-new-army-surveillance-jets-out-of-harms-way</link><description>&lt;p&gt;陆军还认为 ME-11B 发射的无人机大大增强了其深入敌方领土的能力。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/air-launched-drones-key-to-keeping-new-army-surveillance-jets-out-of-harms-way"&gt;空射无人机是保持新陆军侦察机免受伤害的关键，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Apr 2026 21:55:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/air-launched-drones-key-to-keeping-new-army-surveillance-jets-out-of-harms-way</guid></item><item><title>地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-188</link><description>&lt;p&gt;“我期待着亲自消灭你，邦德先生。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-188"&gt;《地堡谈话：让我们谈谈本周我们做过和没有涵盖的所有事情》&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 23:54:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/bunker-talk-lets-talk-about-all-the-things-we-did-and-didnt-cover-this-week-188</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔送给特朗普临时空军一号的747-8i正在进行试飞</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/qatari-747-8i-gifted-to-trump-for-interim-air-force-one-is-undergoing-test-flights</link><description>&lt;p&gt;747 正在紧急投入使用，空军现在表示预计将于今年夏天交付。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/qatari-747-8i-gifted-to-trump-for-interim-air-force-one-is-undergoing-test-flights"&gt;卡塔尔送给特朗普用于临时空军一号的 747-8i 后正在进行试飞，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 23:20:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/qatari-747-8i-gifted-to-trump-for-interim-air-force-one-is-undergoing-test-flights</guid></item><item><title>伊朗重新开放霍尔木兹海峡，美国继续封锁（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-reopens-strait-of-hormuz-u-s-blockade-continues</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这些举措出台之际，特朗普声称美国正在帮助伊朗清除海峡上的水雷。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-reopens-strait-of-hormuz-u-s-blockade-continues"&gt;伊朗重新开放霍尔木兹海峡后，美国继续封锁（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 22:40:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-reopens-strait-of-hormuz-u-s-blockade-continues</guid></item><item><title>MV-75 将可通过套件重新配置以执行医疗后送任务，而不是像 HH-60 那样专门构建</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/mv-75-will-be-reconfigurable-for-medevac-mission-via-kit-not-purpose-built-like-hh-60</link><description>&lt;p&gt;夏安II的速度和航程将迎来美国陆军“除尘”医疗后送能力的重大飞跃。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/mv-75-will-be-reconfigurable-for-medevac-mission-via-kit-not-purpose-built-like-hh-60"&gt;MV-75 将通过套件重新配置用于医疗后送任务，而不是像 HH-60 那样专门建造，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 17:25:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/mv-75-will-be-reconfigurable-for-medevac-mission-via-kit-not-purpose-built-like-hh-60</guid></item><item><title>YFQ-44狂怒战斗机无人机完成有争议的操作测试，可能会加速其部署</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/yfq-44-fury-fighter-drone-wraps-contested-operations-test-that-could-accelerate-its-fielding</link><description>&lt;p&gt;“今天战士手中 85% 的解决方案比永远无法实现的 100% 解决方案要好得多。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/yfq-44-fury-fighter-drone-wraps-contested-operations-test-that-could-accelerate-its-fielding"&gt;YFQ-44 狂怒战斗机无人机包裹有争议的作战测试，可以加速其部署，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 17 Apr 2026 17:22:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/yfq-44-fury-fighter-drone-wraps-contested-operations-test-that-could-accelerate-its-fielding</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰证明廉价拦截无人机可以保护美军免受伊朗沙希德袭击</title><link>https://www.twz.com/land/cheap-interceptor-drones-proven-in-ukraine-protected-u-s-troops-against-iranian-shaheds</link><description>&lt;p&gt;陆军高级官员赞扬了 Merops 无人机在防御伊朗远程神风特攻队无人机方面的表现。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/land/cheap-interceptor-drones-proven-in-ukraine-protected-u-s-troops-against-iranian-shaheds"&gt;乌克兰证明廉价拦截无人机保护美军免受伊朗沙赫德袭击的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 23:22:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/land/cheap-interceptor-drones-proven-in-ukraine-protected-u-s-troops-against-iranian-shaheds</guid></item><item><title>除了封锁之外，美国还在世界各地追捕与伊朗有关的船只（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-pursuing-iranian-linked-ships-all-over-the-world-as-part-of-its-blockade</link><description>&lt;p&gt;参谋长联席会议主席表示，美国现在正在全球范围内努力追捕与支持伊朗有关的船只。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-pursuing-iranian-linked-ships-all-over-the-world-as-part-of-its-blockade"&gt;美国除封锁外还在世界各地追捕与伊朗有关的船只（更新）&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 22:55:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/u-s-pursuing-iranian-linked-ships-all-over-the-world-as-part-of-its-blockade</guid></item><item><title>适应性超强的 Mayhem 10 蜂群无人机由 Switchblade 演变而来</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/super-adaptable-mayhem-10-swarming-drone-evolved-from-the-switchblade</link><description>&lt;p&gt;AeroVironment 的 Mayhem 10 是高度模块化的，可以搜索并摧毁敌方雷达、干扰通信、侦察机、攻击装甲等。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/super-adaptable-mayhem-10-swarming-drone-evolved-from-the-switchblade"&gt;由弹簧刀演变而来的超级适应性混乱 10 蜂群无人机&lt;/a&gt;首次出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;中。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 21:15:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/super-adaptable-mayhem-10-swarming-drone-evolved-from-the-switchblade</guid></item><item><title>陆军关注无人机加油机为其新型 MV-75 Cheyenne II 倾转旋翼机加油</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/army-eyes-drone-tankers-to-refuel-its-new-mv-75-cheyenne-ii-tiltrotors</link><description>&lt;p&gt;陆军和贝尔公司以美国海军的 MQ-25 Stingray 无人加油机为例，展示了即将推出的产品。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/army-eyes-drone-tankers-to-refuel-its-new-mv-75-cheyenne-ii-tiltrotors"&gt;陆军注视无人机加油机为其新型 MV-75 Cheyenne II 倾转旋翼机加油&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 18:48:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/army-eyes-drone-tankers-to-refuel-its-new-mv-75-cheyenne-ii-tiltrotors</guid></item></channel></rss>